title: Minouche Shafik
added: She was created '''Baroness Shafik''', ''of Camden in the London Borough of Camden and of Alexandria in the Arab Republic of Egypt'', in the [[2020 Political Honours]] and was introduced to the [[House of Lords]] on 15 October 2020.<ref>{{London Gazette|issue=28398|page=1610|date=2 October 2020|city=e}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/906078/Political_Peerages_2020.pdf|title=Political Peerages 2020|website=GOV.UK|date=31 July 2020}}</ref>
